And I believe in them as he does.

944
01:01:57,870 --> 01:02:00,340
那就是为何我曾为捍卫它们而战
That's why I went and fought to protect them.

945
01:02:01,510 --> 01:02:04,740
这就是我所思所为，因为如果不是为此
It's what I thought I was doing because if it wasn't for that

946
01:02:04,740 --> 01:02:07,770
