then I have no idea what the hell I was doing there, sir.

947
01:02:09,680 --> 01:02:11,280
谢谢你，下士多斯
Thank you Corporal Doss.

948
01:02:13,950 --> 01:02:15,480
让我看看这信
Let me have the letter.

949
01:02:23,250 --> 01:02:24,250
你得离开
You must go.

